          alt="Writing intentions and releasing the past" 
          class="rounded-xl shadow-xl relative z-10 w-full h-[500px] object-cover -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-[#243c5a] mb-6">For the new to enter, the old must leave</h2>
        <p class="text-[#243c5a]/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          We often try to build new habits or attract opportunities on foundations loaded with fears, doubts, and stagnant energy from the past. It's like trying to plant in a field full of weeds.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#243c5a]/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          This ritual is a powerful, conscious pause. We use ancestral tools to transmute what weighs you down and create the fertile space your true desires need to flourish.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#5d5a8c]">
            <span class="text-xl">üå¨Ô∏è</span> Mental and emotional lightness
