    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-[#243c5a] mb-4">The transformation process</h2>
      <p class="text-[#243c5a]/60">Three phases designed to reset your energy.</p>
