    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-xl text-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group border-b-4 border-[#5d5a8c]/20 hover:border-[#6ed8d9]">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#5d5a8c]/10 group-hover:bg-[#6ed8d9]/20 transition-colors rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl">ü™µ</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-[#243c5a] mb-3">The Cleansing (Fire)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#243c5a]/70">We acknowledge and write down what no longer serves. We use sacred fire (literal or symbolic) and smudging to transmute dense energy.</p>
